{"tid":2155901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商務部:大灣區等地開展數字人民幣試點 先由深圳等地開始","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T10:33:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ded4135611529404bd582dac538219041995731b","tid":2155901,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"商務部發布深化服務貿易創新發展試點方案，明確在京津冀、長三角、粵港澳大灣區及中西部具備條件的試點地區開展數字人民幣試點。<br />\n<br />\n根據方案，人民銀行制訂政策保障措施，先由深圳、成都、蘇州、雄安新區等地及未來冬奧場景相關部門協助推進，後續視乎情況擴大到其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n《21世紀經濟報道》本月初引述消息稱，人民銀行已要求工行(01398)、中行(03988)、農行(01288)和建行(00939)四大內銀在深圳等地作內部測試，各銀行會推出一個名為「數字人民幣」的應用程式(App)，惟考慮到用量及系統負荷等因素，現時有關應用程式還未能公開下載。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2552281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2552281&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b9600691\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2552281</a>"},{"pid":"a87964adc23eee186aca1d0450c61c7b5e301467","tid":2155901,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"羅家聰：現在什麼內循環的一大戲肉 是人幣數碼化 不要低估中國速度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2146990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2146990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1dfd801a5ae47048032b14ffed9ac4759d49df03","tid":2155901,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"你個app係咪得apk檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a4e420808ed9d58610c62abe7630d0a69975a0","tid":2155901,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dfd801a5ae47048032b14ffed9ac4759d49df03","tid":2155901,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"你個app係咪得apk檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img 